Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍬形蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼  相生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼您來的這麼早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我值班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你來幫忙倒一下垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  絕對不要對大家說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不一定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太殘忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好險好險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.05,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(400,00)\bord15\shad0\be50\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N97
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我試著做了果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要嘗嘗看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  怎麼突然做這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我之前不是把你的橘子醬用完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐居然做果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你稍微有點女人味了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  你來猜猜這是什麼果醬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  那我就嘗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃  難吃  難吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃到我都不知道自己在做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  美緒  有俄羅斯紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙  好燙  除了好燙這茶還好難喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃  難吃  難吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  美緒  用果醬冷卻舌頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃  難吃  難吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃  難吃  難吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水  水  水…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶！  牛奶奶奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美緒  那裡面我放了剩下的果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼啊  這無與倫比的難吃感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好難吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難吃  難吃  難吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  美緒你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太難吃了  我都看到微妙的人生走馬燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想到可能會難吃  但沒想到居然有這樣的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道難吃為什麼還要做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為總覺得會很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個笨蛋姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再問一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼味道的果醬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你肯定放了壞掉的魚之類的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  差點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正解是鹹魚乾果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最初也是最後的鹹魚乾紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
