Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天爸爸回得晚  我們叫速食
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼想吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂七八糟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  說了一遍又一遍還是不收拾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不發脾氣就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.00,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(400,00)\bord10\shad0\be40\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N98
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}乙烯樹脂DVD  創刊65周年特大號  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:23.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一開始就疑問滿載
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:31.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}撲通撲通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這這這莫莫莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過不要擅自進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次你要是再進來我就那個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把你那個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}桃源鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢  今天得好好發一次脾氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了不要擅自進來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  為什麼你要擅自打掃別人房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為小誠你總是不打掃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很完美啊  這樣就很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不要進我房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說為什麼你要擅自進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這種東西  姐姐我覺得太早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這種東西  姐姐我覺得太早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這種東西  姐姐我覺得太早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:57.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這種東西  這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你那個  那那那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這是在小誠你的房間發現的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  我才沒看過那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不知道是什麼時候決定這是我的房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不一定是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我覺得你看這個還是太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  你說什麼啊  我完全聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不知道你在說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把這個丟掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是部長的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要扔掉別人的東西嗎  你沒有真的考慮這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我剛才稍微看了下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知該說是讓人驚異呢還是該怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這種東西還是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得會變成不良少年的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我不看好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不看所以你也別擅自進人家房間啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是最糟的事態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼高崎老師會喜歡這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠你生氣了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至少敲個門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我只是想你是不是有點生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  果然生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒生氣啦  我沒生氣所以你快點出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不敲門的話我就把你那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級那個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我想一個人生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說房間就已經收拾成那個樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本書也不是小誠的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近學校大家的風紀也變差了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在學校我也要振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是輔導老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小誠  我們要叫東西吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要說幾遍你才記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}未來發展調查表  班級：1年Q班  名字：相生祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}現在有興趣的事：地球溫暖化  少子高齡化  將來的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  關於將來的希望這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論填目標還是夢想都行  沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在死之前上次電視
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  不是那種事情  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像問得不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有什麼想做的工作或者職業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  這樣啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想  我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為像櫻井老師一樣的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起傳遞的帶子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了哦  中村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們退役之前的最後一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡時定大學中途棄權了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去名乃家的路上遇到博士了  還被狗咬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們下次還會去的  幫我們和博士說下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:28.10,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(400,400)\bord10\shad0\be60\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N99
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  請來當我們的顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不當就是不當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  之前不是說OK嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我什麼時候說過那種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  你真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是和老師比賽還約好了我贏了的話就來當顧問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是那個時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  那個時候是兩敗俱傷未分勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我要把你喜歡我姐姐的事對大家說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團室在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  今天開始圍棋足球部就開始活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起  我突然開門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  我把新的顧問老師帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…等一下啦  為什麼要逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  居然走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明等下還要去拉人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井不在的話就不能正經地介紹我們社團呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣這都是我的社團嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:53.68,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,280)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N100
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我心直跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是小菲你心直跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為等下就要去告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那個叫中之條的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！在這和平的學校的那種朋克精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然莫西幹頭有魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是魅力  倒不如說是有個性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  高崎老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣熾熱的圍棋足球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經久違了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得只有老師你才適合做顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  就算我也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  因為各種原因  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢  因為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  怎麼說呢  因為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  明明都去社團室了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到這個後  你還能說那樣的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣  這是我姐姐高中時代的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧老師  你要怎樣決定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要以此作為交換來成為我們的顧問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要到垂涎三尺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是有了這個  總覺得的某些重要的東西會崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不是最好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都做了什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  那麼你的意思是會來當顧問的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是差勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為老師竟然做出不該有的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我作為教師  同時也是一匹餓狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能棄卒保車了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的話就要拿到全國第一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  從今天起圍棋足球部就開始活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始我會嚴格管教你們的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問中之條在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之條君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之條君  有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅力全無…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你來替我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:08.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}油漆未乾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨時停車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.85,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,340)\fad(400,00)\bord17\shad0\be80\3c&HFFFFFF&}誰\N來\N救\N救\N我\N吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水上同學  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來找你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.73,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(665,270)\fad(400,00)\bord10\shad0\be50\3c&HFFFFFF&}日\N常\N之\N101
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  讓你費心帶了這麼多點心來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是讓狗來咬博士的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去泡個茶就回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本傳說中五大明王之一，守護西方，六面六臂六足。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大威德明王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不帥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}36室帶餐廳廚房。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36LDK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有浴室有廁所沒有窗戶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在畫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大青鯊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你畫點其他樣子的鯊魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫個笑著的鯊魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和博士畫的交換好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等…
